<br>
Producing a roleplaying server is just so simple. You just don't allow certain things and I think the polite suggestion from a GM who can move you that maybe another server would be more appropriate is just the thing. <br>
<br>
And it avoids the vicious bloodbath that's coming on FV when players are forced to enforce RPing through shunning tactics, etc. You can already see the nastiness--I'm certainly engaged in it--I shouldn't have to be, VI should be doing this.<br>
<br>
